**2e. 新增 writeOperationLog 私有方法**

在 `getWorkExperienceByIndex` 方法前新增：
```php
private function writeOperationLog(int $recProId, int $workExperienceIndex, string $reason, ?string $specificReason): void
{
    try {
        $reasonLabel = match ($reason) {
            BackgroundCheckRecordMd::SKIP_OFFLINE => '转为线下背调方式，并已登记上传到录用材料中',
            BackgroundCheckRecordMd::SKIP_NO_NEED => '无需背调',
            BackgroundCheckRecordMd::SKIP_DEFERRED => '候选人暂未离职，将在入职前完成背调流程',
            default => $reason,
        };
        $detail = "倒数第{$workExperienceIndex}段工作经历背调处理：{$reasonLabel}";
        if ($reason === BackgroundCheckRecordMd::SKIP_NO_NEED && $specificReason) {
            $detail .= "，具体原因：{$specificReason}";
        }
        $service = app(\App\Service\ResumeOperationService::class);
        $service->recordByType(
            $recProId,
            'recruitment_procession',
            'background_check_skip',
            '',
            $detail,
            '',
            ['rec_pro_id' => $recProId]
        );
    } catch (\Throwable $e) {
        // 日志写入失败不影响主流程
        \Illuminate\Support\Facades\Log::warning('BackgroundCheckReminderService::writeOperationLog failed: ' . $e->getMessage());
    }
}
```

